Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.59,0:00:04.10,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Rokuro, Saizo, Isanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.56,0:00:07.77,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,The three of you will \Naccompany me to the capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.22,0:00:10.19,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of you will stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.19,0:00:11.86,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,What? The rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:13.36,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:17.91,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Ana, I'm sure the nights \Nwill be very lonely for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.91,0:00:20.54,Brave-Main,ANA,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be lonely at all. Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.74,0:00:23.46,Brave-Main,ANA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.49,0:00:25.52,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:26.73,Brave-Main,ANA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:29.17,Brave-Main,SASUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Yukimura-sama, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:32.04,Brave-Main,SASUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:34.55,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you acting all \Nhigh and mighty, monkey?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:38.42,Brave-Main,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,But Isanami will be worried \Nif I do not accompany her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.42,0:00:40.35,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I've got Saizo. I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.35,0:00:42.02,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:44.81,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be so bored without Saizo, I'd rot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:47.29,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna fight Saizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:48.44,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You're so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:49.86,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:52.56,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,He's just like a girl in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:01:00.87,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,The power to destroy all living things...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:36.59,Ep-Title,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,Sword and Fan
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:42.80,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,The weather's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:44.90,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Sit still. You're jostling the horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:50.22,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you think we look \Nlike a princess and a lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:51.50,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:54.01,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem? You're no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:56.42,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how everyone else is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:59.14,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Some of them didn't seem \Ntoo happy about staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:01.21,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Ana must be \Ncrying from loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.21,0:03:04.92,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,Kamanosuke and Seikai were\Ncomplaining until the moment we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:09.12,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who's gonna be at the tea ceremony\Nwe're attending in the capitol?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:14.87,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Primarily Maeda, Mori, Uesugi, \Nand the rest of the Five Elders.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:19.05,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,We might even get to see Ishida\NMitsunari and Naoe Kanetsugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.39,0:03:21.51,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and that dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:24.98,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the one-eyed lord \Nof Oshu will be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.59,0:03:28.45,Brave-Main,TSUNEMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,My lord, are you going dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:31.48,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am. \NAppearances are important.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:34.96,Brave-Main,KOJURO,0000,0000,0000,,But you'd have to be stupid to \Ngo dressed so flamboyantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:36.36,Brave-Main,KOJURO,0000,0000,0000,,Please have more respect for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:38.19,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:41.15,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,When I said appearances, \NI didn't mean my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:43.13,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,I meant my attitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:47.33,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to make a good first impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:50.54,Brave-Main,KOJURO,0000,0000,0000,,With Sanada Yukimura?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:56.01,Brave-Main,KOJURO,0000,0000,0000,,Sanada, the man hiding \Nthe Kushimitama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.01,0:03:59.21,Brave-Main,KOJURO,0000,0000,0000,,My lord, do you plan to do \Nanything in the capitol?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:03.81,Brave-Main,TSUNEMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,If you and Ieyasu both attempt \Nto claim the Kushimitama,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:05.21,Brave-Main,TSUNEMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,won't it attract too much attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:06.65,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:10.67,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,I told the old man that \Neverything he's heard was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:12.96,Brave-Main,TSUNEMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,You told him it was a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:15.84,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:19.65,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,I promised I'd make it up to him by\Nputting on a show for him at the capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:22.30,Brave-Main,KOJURO,0000,0000,0000,,My lord, what are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:26.00,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to meeting \Nyou, Sanada Yukimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:30.24,Brave-Note,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Food
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:30.79,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:32.84,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You always eat so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:35.27,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys heading up the road?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:37.26,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, youngster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:39.92,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,We intend to. Is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:41.66,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:43.92,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,The road ahead's been \Nwashed out by the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:45.50,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you from around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:48.07,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's a bit further,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:50.05,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,but you should take the \Nmountain pass over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:51.74,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:52.53,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:54.68,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do, my lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:56.28,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:57.44,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:04:58.55,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:00.15,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:02.84,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's to thank you \Nfor your directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:04.21,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Isanami, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:04.86,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:07.62,Brave-Italic,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of gunpowder?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:10.83,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:13.29,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,See you later, youngster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:22.55,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,She fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:24.59,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,She's so innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:25.82,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,What's innocent about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.00,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,She just follows her natural urges.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:29.80,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,She's way too relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:32.04,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:34.68,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,No one's trying to attack us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:37.27,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,We're traveling with an obvious target.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:39.54,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,I did not expect you to bring her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:44.96,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it'd be more fun \Nto have her along.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:45.88,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:52.57,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we're all you're \Nbringing to the capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:53.83,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,How cheap are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:58.49,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of bringing an entourage\Nfor the sake of appearances,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.49,0:06:01.67,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer traveling with you three.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:06.13,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,The wind feels wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.53,0:06:08.49,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You're a strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:11.60,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You're more of a playboy than a lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:16.14,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,Lord, please do not cause any trouble\Nwith the women in the capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:17.30,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:19.65,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,That place is nothing without \Ntheir entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:21.81,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your only source of enjoyment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:22.80,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:23.61,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.81,0:06:26.53,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:28.82,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Rokuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:31.20,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:34.16,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:35.37,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Isanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:36.29,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.34,0:06:40.50,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:45.92,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,It's a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:48.63,Brave-Main,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,Isanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:57.10,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:01.56,Brave-Main,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,Your big brother's arrived. \NAll is well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:02.81,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:04.98,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.21,0:07:10.95,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Isanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:13.41,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.36,Brave-Main,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,Isanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:27.25,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:28.96,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pull you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:30.63,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:31.84,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Isanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:32.74,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:38.40,Brave-Italic,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.80,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,You owe me one, Saizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:54.02,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Kamanosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:56.47,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:57.68,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Can't I be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:07:59.49,Brave-Main,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,Isanami, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:00.00,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:02.11,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like everyone's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:05.25,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,But who would do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:06.96,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:11.01,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,You're the first ones \Nto avoid all my traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:14.22,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're the boy from the inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:19.29,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,That gunpowder I smelled...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:20.89,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You did all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:22.22,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,That settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:23.94,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, hire me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:25.31,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.90,0:08:36.24,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,You want to become a samurai,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:39.79,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,so you've been testing potential\Nmasters by sending them this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:42.70,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,I'll choose my own master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:44.42,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna work for some weakling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:48.11,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,You all passed my test. I'll serve you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:49.36,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,We passed, did we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:53.24,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,No one sets better traps or \Nmakes better explosives than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:54.09,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,I can be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:55.22,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:58.16,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your decision, brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:09:00.67,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,Wah, miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:02.98,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo, don't bully children.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:04.20,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:06.09,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,He almost killed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:08.94,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No one was hurt. Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.89,0:09:12.98,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Go home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.98,0:09:14.72,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Your parents must be worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:15.86,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:16.68,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:19.16,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any parents. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:21.43,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,I've always lived by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:24.49,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,I bet your parents abandoned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:25.96,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,It's not uncommon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:27.32,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo, that's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:28.29,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Say whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:30.52,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:32.50,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I will allow you to serve me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:33.96,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:35.81,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yukimura-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:37.43,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crazy, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:40.73,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a lot of guts for a \Nyoung boy, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:42.33,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:44.38,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,What is your name, youngster?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:45.68,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,Mochizuki Rokuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.95,0:09:48.73,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the sixth child, \Nso that's why I'm Rokuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:50.80,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,I chose my own family name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:55.07,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be convenient having \Ntwo men with the same name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:57.15,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,We really do have the same name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:10:00.00,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you call him that earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:02.41,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what you call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:04.75,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,Rokuro's a lame name, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:11.92,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Lameness aside, there's \Nonly one Rokuro for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:16.01,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Benmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:19.24,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, your \Nname is Benmaru. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:20.12,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:21.20,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What a cute name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:24.15,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, Benmaru was your childhood name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:25.39,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:26.94,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be angry, Rokuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.94,0:10:30.95,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I say I admire the boy's courage?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:34.40,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, no encounter \Nis mere coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:35.69,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:39.27,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:45.24,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Benmaru, I will give \Nyou your first order.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.00,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:48.82,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,We're on our way to the capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:51.07,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Because I cannot take you with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:53.84,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to wait \Nat the inn up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:55.30,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:59.15,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,You must obey this order \Nif you wish to serve me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:00.10,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:01.14,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:03.80,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,And you two should return to Ueda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:07.47,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's what I'd like to say, \Nbut I know you won't listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:08.41,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:10.27,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:37.22,Brave-Main,PEOPLE,0000,0000,0000,,What extravagant clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:39.09,Brave-Main,PEOPLE,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he's Lord Date.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:41.83,Brave-Main,PEOPLE,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, from Oshu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:44.76,Brave-Main,NIKO,0000,0000,0000,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:47.88,Brave-Main,NIKO,0000,0000,0000,,My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:49.24,Brave-Main,ICHIMARU,0000,0000,0000,,You must have had a long journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:51.44,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Ichimaru, Niko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:53.44,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for meeting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:57.87,Brave-Main,NIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Did you walk through the \Ncapitol in those clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.87,0:11:59.44,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,It suits me, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.36,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:03.11,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Has Lord Date Masamune arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:04.32,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:06.41,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,With the tea ceremony tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:08.20,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,I have come to deliver a special decree.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:09.04,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,What decree?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:11.25,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,A weapons ban?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:12.56,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:14.55,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,The decree has been issued \Nthroughout the capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:17.96,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,While I am gone, you must \Nnot draw your weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:21.66,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,What are we supposed to do if we \Nrun into Tokugawa or Date's men?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.66,0:12:24.43,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,As long as the decree is in effect, \Nwe should not be attacked soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:27.60,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch, you ate my food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:29.68,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's your own fault for sleeping late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:31.64,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.95,0:12:35.10,Brave-Main,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,You will not hurt Isanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:37.84,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm more worried about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:40.08,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, playboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:44.31,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,If I draw my weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.31,0:12:47.41,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Tokugawa will use it as an \Nexcuse to punish Sanada, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:50.72,Brave-Note,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(460,0)}Kitano Shrine
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:57.75,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,You are the only one so underdressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:13:00.85,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care. These clothes \Nare more comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:02.64,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Yukimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:06.59,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Ishida Mitsunari.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:08.60,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you had been invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:13.81,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I could never refuse an invitation \Nfrom the great Tokugawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:16.02,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:17.77,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Surely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:20.32,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,You are a difficult man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:22.19,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,You flatter me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:26.94,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,When I sent you a secret message\Nregarding Ieyasu's behavior,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:28.40,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,you did nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:32.16,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,Now Ieyasu is attempting \Nto provoke me into a war,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:33.91,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,and swing the balance in his favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:36.72,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:38.80,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time to establish your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:40.63,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,At least, that was my understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.91,0:13:43.02,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get involved in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:44.12,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:48.95,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, he's been rather brazen since\Nthe father of the regent passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:52.10,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,Even this tea ceremony is nothing \Nmore than a public display of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.61,0:13:54.39,Brave-Main,KANETSUGU,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't agree more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:59.19,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,Naoe-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:02.15,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Kanetsugu, it's \Ngood to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:06.70,Brave-Main,KANETSUGU,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure to see \Nyou again, Yukimura-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:10.57,Brave-Main,KANETSUGU,0000,0000,0000,,Have you already paid your \Nrespects to Lord Ieyasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:12.74,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:15.04,Brave-Main,KANETSUGU,0000,0000,0000,,You should go soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.83,Brave-Main,KANETSUGU,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get to see something \Nquite interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:17.87,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:22.09,Brave-Main,KANETSUGU,0000,0000,0000,,An arrogant little raccoon \Ndog thinks he can speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:23.59,Brave-Main,KANETSUGU,0000,0000,0000,,I almost couldn't believe my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:26.00,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,You're as merciless as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:30.21,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,Raccoon dogs should stay in the \Nmountains where they belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:33.42,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he issued a weapons ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:36.98,Brave-Main,KANETSUGU,0000,0000,0000,,When did he become our leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:40.17,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. We're here for a tea ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:44.07,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's enjoy ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:47.53,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,These sachets are so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:49.82,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Those are pretty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:52.74,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't wander off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.98,0:14:54.36,Brave-Main,NIKO,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Ichimaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:57.75,Brave-Main,ICHIMARU,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is the priestess \Nwe had in the castle prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:58.71,Brave-Main,NIKO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:01.42,Brave-Main,NIKO,0000,0000,0000,,That means the bastards \Naround her are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:03.29,Brave-Main,NIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Sanada's men!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:08.50,Brave-Main,ICHIMARU,0000,0000,0000,,No. Our lord told us \Nthere's a weapons ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:12.60,Brave-Main,NIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying we should \Njust let them go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:14.19,Brave-Main,ICHIMARU,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we invite them for some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:14.97,Brave-Main,NIKO,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:20.53,Brave-Main,IEYASU,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the delay, everyone. \NWe're still awaiting one arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:22.44,Brave-Main,IEYASU,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.24,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,You're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:29.07,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,We're lucky to have \Nsuch beautiful weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:33.28,Brave-Main,IEYASU,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Lord Date. \NWe've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:37.20,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Tokugawa, thank you \Nfor your invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.53,0:15:41.00,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Date, hurry up. \NGo sit next to Lord Sanada.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:15:58.89,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Date!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:01.16,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,There is a weapons ban in effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:02.85,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:07.41,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd show everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:09.86,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,...some swordplay to compensate \Nfor my tardiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:12.95,Brave-Main,IEYASU,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds interesting. I'll allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:17.53,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,The beauty of swordplay comes \Nout when two swords clash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:20.42,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Could I have a volunteer to \Nhelp me with this performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:24.00,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Sanada.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:27.45,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Would you join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.97,0:16:29.75,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,You're too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:31.05,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:33.16,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,While we are honored by your choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:35.30,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,my master does not have \Nhis sword with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:37.01,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be possible for \Nyou to select another?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:40.10,Brave-Main,KOJURO,0000,0000,0000,,I will lend you my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:41.18,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:42.54,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, Rokuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:47.03,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,It would be the pinnacle of\Nimpoliteness to refuse his request.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:50.23,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I will perform with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:07.88,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,On your guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:09.26,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,On your guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:23.17,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,What impressive swordplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:27.31,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,One wrong move and he'll be caught\Non the sharp edge of the blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:33.57,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing that, Lord Sanada \Nmoves accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:34.63,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.00,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.58,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:47.54,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,My feet can't keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:51.57,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yukimura? \NYou look like a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:54.76,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,They seem fast enough to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:58.97,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:02.14,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,you can't run forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:16.90,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:29.00,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,How unsightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:31.93,Brave-Main,IEYASU,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:34.16,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,Yukimura, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:36.47,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:39.69,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:46.90,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Date's swordplay scared \Nmy feet out from under me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.35,0:18:55.36,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:58.00,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,All that movement has made me thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:19:00.07,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Could I get some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:07.08,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,That was quite the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:10.17,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,People will be talking about that raccoon\Ndog's expression for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:15.88,Brave-Main,KANETSUGU,0000,0000,0000,,Masamune must be furious to \Nbe brushed off like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.47,0:19:19.95,Brave-Main,KANETSUGU,0000,0000,0000,,What an embarrassment \Nfor the dragon of Oshu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:22.34,Brave-Main,KANETSUGU,0000,0000,0000,,That was quite the mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.67,0:19:25.30,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,You've always got nasty \Nthings to say, Kanetsugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:28.31,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you escaped so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:31.65,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? \NThat wasn't easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:32.70,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Sanada.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:37.04,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message for \NLord Sanada regarding...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:38.69,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,...the incident at the tea ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:42.68,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,You are to go up to Fushimi Castle\Nimmediately and make an appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:43.41,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:46.55,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,That's completely unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:49.84,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,If you do not go, \Nthere will be consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:50.87,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:53.00,Brave-Main,KANETSUGU,0000,0000,0000,,How one-sided.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:55.77,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,With all of Tokugawa's \Nsupporters against you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:57.53,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,you won't be able to talk \Nyour way out of that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:19:59.78,Brave-Main,KANETSUGU,0000,0000,0000,,That must be their aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:02.48,Brave-Main,KANETSUGU,0000,0000,0000,,They'll either take your lands \Nor have you kill yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:04.91,Brave-Main,MITSUNARI,0000,0000,0000,,Yukimura, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.17,0:20:08.31,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ignore it, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:10.86,Brave-Main,KOJURO,0000,0000,0000,,He got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.41,0:20:15.25,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,You noticed his footwork, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:16.40,Brave-Main,KOJURO,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:18.80,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,He's an interesting one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:21.70,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,That slippery fellow's got me excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:25.58,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,He looked like he was smiling,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:27.64,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,but I could see the boldness in his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.64,0:20:29.38,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,He's more than what he seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:31.28,Brave-Main,NIKO,0000,0000,0000,,My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:32.43,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.43,0:20:35.02,Brave-Main,NIKO,0000,0000,0000,,The priestess who escaped from us...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:37.84,Brave-Main,NIKO,0000,0000,0000,,...is with Sanada's men here in the capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:40.21,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,The Kushimitama is in the capitol?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.15,0:20:43.58,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:45.31,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,He can't have gone far!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:45.96,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:47.30,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let Sanada escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:49.26,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:51.65,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we going back to Ueda now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:53.50,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even get to buy souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:56.23,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies, Isanami. \NYou can get them next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:01.43,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he's headed towards Omi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:04.06,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Follow him! Don't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:10.33,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.64,0:21:12.53,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's one of Sanada's men!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.53,0:21:13.94,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:15.60,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:22.66,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.66,0:21:24.24,Brave-Main,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,Better safe than sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:26.01,Brave-Main,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,Taizan Meido!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.77,0:21:30.94,Brave-Main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:32.83,Brave-Main,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,They can't follow us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:33.89,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't draw attention to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:40.05,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,You see? I knew it'd be more \Nfun to bring Isanami along.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.05,0:21:41.15,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.55,0:21:45.08,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.46,0:23:24.42,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that kid doing hiding there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.11,0:23:25.97,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Benmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.97,0:23:27.38,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.38,0:23:28.92,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:31.97,Brave-Main,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,I was just out for a \Nstroll in these woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:35.39,Brave-Main,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect rocks, spears, \Nor fire to come my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.39,0:23:38.72,Brave-Main,SEIKAI,0000,0000,0000,,Gods, I gratefully \Naccept your challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.72,0:23:41.16,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. The pit trap didn't go off.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.16,0:23:43.29,Brave-Main,BENMARU,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I didn't use enough gunpowder.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.29,0:23:44.73,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You're one terrifying kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.57,0:23:48.12,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,The next episode of Brave 10 \Nis "The Birth of a Warrior."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.05,0:23:50.30,Brave-NextEp,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,The Birth of a Warrior
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.12,0:23:49.91,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
